import React from 'react'; import { Box, Typography, TextField, Grid, Paper, Table, TableBody, TableCell, TableContainer, TableHead, TableRow, Checkbox, Button } from '@mui/material'; const ApplicationReportBPT = () => { // Constants for repeated values const SUBJECTS = ['Botany', 'Zoology', 'Physics', 'Chemistry', 'English', 'Second Language']; const DOCUMENTS = [ 'CASTE CERTIFICATE', '10th Class Marks Memo', 'INTERMEDIATE MARKS MEMO', '6TH to 10TH Study and Conduct Certificate', 'INTER STUDY AND CONDUCT CERTIFICATE', 'TRANSFER OR MIGRATION CERTIFICATE of Intermediate', 'TELANGANA STATE EXPECT-2025 RANK CARD' ]; // Initial form state const initialFormData = { // Advertisement Details adNo: '', adDate: '', applicationNo: '', courseName: '', courseCode: '', dateOfEntry: '', lastDate: '', department: '', // Applicant's Details name: '', fatherName: '', dob: '', age: '', placeOfBirth: '', socialStatus: '', nationality: '', maritalStatus: '', gender: '', differentlyAbled: '', mark1: '', mark2: '', universityArea: '', inService: '', aadhar: '', fatherEmail: '', // Address Details correspondenceAddress: '', correspondenceCountry: 'India', correspondenceState: '', correspondenceDistrict: '', correspondencePincode: '', correspondenceMobile: '', correspondenceEmail: '', sameAsCorrespondence: true, permanentAddress: '', permanentCountry: 'India', permanentState: '', permanentDistrict: '', permanentPincode: '', permanentMobile: '', permanentEmail: '', // Parents' Details fatherNameParent: '', fatherAge: '', fatherOccupation: '', motherName: '', motherAge: '', motherOccupation: '', // Intermediate Marks subjects: SUBJECTS.map(subject => ({ subject, y1: '', y2: '', practical: ['Botany', 'Zoology', 'Physics', 'Chemistry'].includes(subject) ? '' : '-', total: '', max: '' })), totalMarks: '', totalPercentage: '', groupTotal: '', groupPercentage: '', // Educational History (7 years) educationHistory: Array(7).fill().map(() => ({ class: '', year: '', school: '', place: '' })), // EAPCET Details eapcetRegNo: '', hallTicketNo: '', rank: '', // Payment Details paymentType: '', transactionId: '', paymentDate: '', bankName: '', branchDetails: '', amount: '', paymentRemarks: '', // Declaration signature: '', declarationDate: '', officeRemarks: '' }; const [formData, setFormData] = React.useState(initialFormData); // Memoized handler for better performance const handleChange = React.useCallback((e) => { const { name, value } = e.target; setFormData(prev => ({ ...prev, [name]: value })); }, []); const handleSubjectChange = React.useCallback((index, field, value) => { setFormData(prev => { const updatedSubjects = [...prev.subjects]; updatedSubjects[index] = { ...updatedSubjects[index], [field]: value }; return { ...prev, subjects: updatedSubjects }; }); }, []); const handleEducationChange = React.useCallback((index, field, value) => { setFormData(prev => { const updatedEducation = [...prev.educationHistory]; updatedEducation[index] = { ...updatedEducation[index], [field]: value }; return { ...prev, educationHistory: updatedEducation }; }); }, []); const handleSameAddressChange = React.useCallback((e) => { const checked = e.target.checked; setFormData(prev => ({ ...prev, sameAsCorrespondence: checked, permanentAddress: checked ? prev.correspondenceAddress : '', permanentCountry: checked ? prev.correspondenceCountry : '', permanentState: checked ? prev.correspondenceState : '', permanentDistrict: checked ? prev.correspondenceDistrict : '', permanentPincode: checked ? prev.correspondencePincode : '', permanentMobile: checked ? prev.correspondenceMobile : '', permanentEmail: checked ? prev.correspondenceEmail : '' })); }, []); const handleSubmit = (e) => { e.preventDefault(); console.log('Form submitted:', formData); // Add your form submission logic here }; // Reusable form section component const FormSection = ({ title, children }) => ( {title} {children} ); // Reusable text field component const FormTextField = ({ name, label, ...props }) => ( ); return ( APPLICATION FORM - Bachelor of Physiotherapy - 2025 {/* Advertisement Details */} {/* Applicant's Details */} {/* Address Details */} {/* Correspondence Address */} Correspondence Address {/* Permanent Address */} Permanent Address {/* Checkbox for same address */} Same as Correspondence Address {/* Parents' Details */} {/* Intermediate Marks */} {formData.subjects.map((item, index) => ( handleSubjectChange(index, 'y1', e.target.value)} fullWidth /> handleSubjectChange(index, 'y2', e.target.value)} fullWidth /> handleSubjectChange(index, 'practical', e.target.value) : undefined} fullWidth InputProps={{ readOnly: item.practical === '-' }} /> handleSubjectChange(index, 'total', e.target.value)} fullWidth /> handleSubjectChange(index, 'max', e.target.value)} fullWidth /> ))} {/* Educational History */} {formData.educationHistory.map((item, index) => ( handleEducationChange(index, 'class', e.target.value)} fullWidth /> handleEducationChange(index, 'year', e.target.value)} fullWidth /> handleEducationChange(index, 'school', e.target.value)} fullWidth /> handleEducationChange(index, 'place', e.target.value)} fullWidth /> ))} {/* EAPCET Details */} {/* Payment Details */} {/* Document Details */} S.No. Document Type {DOCUMENTS.map((type, index) => ( {index + 1} {type} ))}
{/* Declaration */} I declare that the particulars given above are correct. I agree to abide by the admission prospectus issued by the Institute. I also declare that in the event that information provided is incorrect or false. I may be prosecuted as per law. {/* Submit Button */} ); }; export default ApplicationReportBPT;
